/*T.C=O(N)
Ist Approach
1. If array is even add element at i and -element at i+1
2. If array is odd at 0 at n-1 position
Psuedocode:
while(i+1<n){
    arr[i]=elem;
    arr[i+1]=-elem;
    elem++;
    i+=2
}
return arr;
CODE:
        vector<int>result(n);
        int start=1;
        int i=0;
        while(i+1<n){
            result[i]=start;
            result[i+1]=-start;
